ter. Here the error sum of squares (ESS) for cluster c is: , where and , is the sum of squared mean deviations in all years for all industries in the", "start_char_idx": null, "end_char_idx": null, "text_template": "{metadata_str}\n\n{content}", "metadata_template": "{key}: {value}", "metadata_seperator": "\n"}, "__type__": "1"}, "3dd731ef-4167-42b9-871b-476bbb53e6ad": {"__data__": {"id_": "3dd731ef-4167-42b9-871b-476bbb53e6ad", "embedding": null, "metadata": {"Title_URL": "https://www.undp.org/asia-pacific/publications/whos-afraid-industrial-policy", "Author": "United Nations Development Programme", "Publisher": "United Nations Development Programme", "Type": "Report"}, "excluded_embed_metadata_keys": [], "excluded_llm_metadata_keys": [], "relationships": {"1": {"node_id": "Who's Afraid of Industrial Policy?", "node_type": null, "metadata": {"Title_URL": "https://www.undp.org/asia-pacific/publications/whos-afraid-industrial-policy", "Author": "United Nations Development Programme", "Publisher": "United Nations Development Programme", "Type": "Report"}, "hash": "d10b0c994d8e10b67fd7ba09d972a7e318bfc491403f3e8f903d73213db1d9b5"}}, "hash": "d10b0c994d8e10b67fd7ba09d972a7e318bfc491403f3e8f903d73213db1d9b5", "text": "cth cluster, is the sum of mean deviations of wages at time t for industries in the cth cluster, is the number of industries in cluster c, and is the mean deviation of wage at time t for the ith industry among industries in the cth cluster. Following these, in order to test whether Ward\u2019s clustering method gives appropriate results the average linkage method is applied for comparison. Since both methods give the same results it can be concluded that the results passed the assessments tests.36 36 For more details, see Galbraith and Lu (2001) and Kaufman and Rousseeuw (1990). Asia-Pacific Trade and Investment Initiative Regional Centre in Colombo 23 Independence Avenue Colombo 7 Sri Lanka Tel: +94 11 4526400 Fax: +94 11 4526410 Email: asiapacific.trade@u